</problem>
<solution id="fs-idp268325184"><para id="fs-idp268325312">(a) ClO<sub>2</sub>; (b) N<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub>; (c) K<sub>3</sub>P; (d) Ag<sub>2</sub>S; (e) AIF<sub>3</sub>·3H<sub>2</sub>O; (f) SiO<sub>2</sub></para>
